<item chapterid="608496" siteid="0" sourceid="0" sourcecid="0" sourcecorder="0" articleid="1945" articlename="一号特卫" volumeid="0" posterid="1" poster="admin" postdate="1521889296" lastupdate="1521889296" chaptername="第122章灾难来临前的征兆" chapterorder="121" size="6686" saleprice="0" salenum="0" totalcost="0" attachment="" summary="    正在这时候，杨丽娜的手机铃声响了起来。

